---
title: Caribbean Stew with Thyme-Roasted Carrots, Spinach Callaloo and Naan Bread
description: We're dreaming of a beach holiday with this Caribbean-inspired recipe! Creamy stew is served with sweet roasted carrots and a traditional Trinidadian leafy green dish, callaloo (we're making ours with spinach.) We can hear the steel drums already...
